data.description: Come and check out this Beautiful up to date home that is sitting on 1.26 Acres. This is located 2 minutes off Johnston Street. This home has epoxy flooring throughout, updated cabinets and granite countertops. It has 2 dining and 2 Living rooms. This home also has 3 bathrooms in total with 2 of them connected to bedrooms. With a little TLC, this would make a great home to raise your family in.
